name: Corsica-Corset 2021
description:
This piece is an iteration of Corseticus 2016 a transparent layered collage I created after I had back surgery in 2015.The collage on 24 x 36”canvas with digital bordering. 

Sound design by long-time friend and musical genius @fendelmarc 
Instruments: Frame drum, Elektron Model Samples, LABS, flutes, cassette tape players, gongs, & silver earrings. 
Vocal samples: Reyna Zack 
Recorded and mixed in Seattle -  August 2021 

Anne Grgich is one of the most original and innovative artists in the group of American artists known as Outsiders. Completely self-taught and in Raw Vision Magazine Woman Issue #103 by Colin Rhodes. 
  
The original art can be found at ZQ Art Gallery:
https://www.artsy.net/artwork/anne-grgich-corseticus
